casebody.data:
Salvatore J. MORETTI, Appellant-Petitioner,
v.
BERGEN COUNTY PROSECUTOR'S OFFICE, Respondent-Respondent. C-852 September Term 2018
082450 Supreme Court of New Jersey. May 14, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-002807-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied; and it is further

ORDERED that the notice of appeal is dismissed.
